---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Hot Water Heaters"
  description={`Hot water heater repair, replacement and installation in Asheville & Hendersonville, NC, including tankless. Same-day service often available. Call ${site.phone}.`}
  heroTitle="Get Hot Water When You Need It"
  heroSubtitle="Schedule hot water heater repair in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC."
  heroImage="/images/gallery/gallery-01.jpg"
  listHeading="3 signs your hot water heater needs service"
  listItems={[
    'It needs to be repaired frequently',
    'It takes a long time to heat your water',
    "It's more than 15 years old",
  ]}
  listNote="Get in touch with Nesbitt's Plumbing in Asheville or Hendersonville, NC for hot water heater repair or replacement."
  ctaHeading="Need Water Heater Repair or Replacement?"
>
  <p>
    There are few things worse than coming home after a long day for a nice, hot shower and
    finding out that there's no hot water. Count on Nesbitt's Plumbing for expert hot water
    heater repair in Asheville &amp; Hendersonville, North Carolina. We offer convenient same-day
    services.
  </p>
  <p>
    Call now to schedule an appointment for water heater repair or other plumbing services:
    <a href={site.phoneHref} class="font-semibold text-drop-600 hover:underline">{site.phone}</a>.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you're constantly dealing with hot water issues in your home or office, you need hot water
    heater repair or replacement in the Asheville or Hendersonville, NC area. We handle sales,
    installation, service, repair and replacement, including gas and tankless water heaters.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
